author: Ubisoft
description:
It’s a premiere in Trackmania: we’re thrilled to welcome Visa BoursoBank!
For this occasion, ZeratoR is back in the game and has created 5 special Weekly Shorts for the very first time.
The tracks go FREE for everyone on PC and consoles on Sun Oct 12 – 18:00 CEST.
Plus: 3 stunning new car skins!


About Trackmania: 
Experience the thrills of racing and the joy of creating your own tracks with Trackmania®! 
Trackmania® combines easy-to-learn, hard-to-master gameplay with a wide diversity of tracks, in addition to regular seasons & live events: 
Play in an online multiplayer environment or solo against players' ghosts. Progress through rankings and collectible medals. 
Face new challenges with the Weekly Shorts, a new season every 3 months and a wide variety of community tracks displayed in the ""Track of the Day"" selection. 
#Ubisoft #Trackmania

About Ubisoft: 
Ubisoft is a creator of worlds, committed to enriching players’ lives with original and memorable entertainment experiences.
